  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="letter">
        <salute>Dear Rev. King:</salute>
        <p>
          It is impossible to express the shock and grief I felt when you were hurt. It is good to hear that you <del rend="strikethrough">have a chance</del> are recovering, but I am sorry you have to suffer because of an insane, wanton act. I have read your book and liked it very much. Your mention of me is a great compli-ment that I appreciate.
        </p>
      </div>
